PN,41901
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1778602268
OL,3,CBA Pilot who bludgeoned wife to death
OL,4,Cand dumped her body in park, denied
OL,5,Cparole
OL,7,FA former British Airways captain who
OL,8,Fbludgeoned his wife to death will be
OL,9,Fkept behind bars, having refused to
OL,10,Fgive evidence at his own parole
OL,11,Fhearing.
OL,13,FRobert Brown will remain in prison
OL,14,Fafter a Parole Board panel heard that
OL,15,Fhe has done no risk-reduction work
OL,16,Fwhile in jail and refuses to accept
OL,17,Fthat he poses any risk to the public.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1778602268
OL,3,CBA Pilot who bludgeoned wife to death
OL,4,Cand dumped her body in park, denied
OL,5,Cparole
OL,7,FThe former pilot attacked his wife
OL,8,FJoanna Simpson, 46, with a claw hammer
OL,9,Fin their Berkshire family home in
OL,10,FOctober 2010 as their two young
OL,11,Fchildren cowered in a playroom.
OL,13,FHe killed her a week before their
OL,14,Fdivorce was due to be finalised and
OL,15,Fdumped her body in a makeshift coffin
OL,16,Fin Windsor Great Park.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1778602268
OL,3,CBA Pilot who bludgeoned wife to death
OL,4,Cand dumped her body in park, denied
OL,5,Cparole
OL,7,FThe parole panel found that there was
OL,8,F"no sufficient evidence that his risk
OL,9,Fhad reduced since he was sentenced"
OL,10,Fand that he could not be managed in
OL,11,Fthe community.
OL,13,FBrown was jailed for 26 years in 2011
OL,14,Fafter being cleared of murder but he
OL,15,Fadmitted manslaughter on the grounds
OL,16,Fof diminished responsibility. A
OL,17,Fpsychiatric report said he suffered
OL,18,Ffrom an "adjustment disorder".
OL,26,@pD@AOUqD@cO]zD@IOUzD@]O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1778602268
OL,3,CBA Pilot who bludgeoned wife to death
OL,4,Cand dumped her body in park, denied
OL,5,Cparole
OL,7,FReferring to prison courses designed
OL,8,Fto reduce risk, the parole panel
OL,9,Ffound: "Overall it was clear that
OL,10,FRobert Brown has not been willing to
OL,11,Fengage except on his own terms, which
OL,12,Fusually means not engaging at all.
OL,14,F"The panel's conclusion was that
OL,15,FRobert Brown does not appear to accept
OL,16,Fany element of retained culpability,
OL,17,Falthough he says he accepts full
OL,18,Fresponsibility for what he did.
OL,26,@qD@HOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1778602268
OL,3,CBA Pilot who bludgeoned wife to death
OL,4,Cand dumped her body in park, denied
OL,5,Cparole
OL,7,F"His expressed view is that he only
OL,8,Foffended because of a mental illness,
OL,9,Fthe adjustment disorder; the
OL,10,Fadjustment disorder had passed by the
OL,11,Ftime he was sentenced (which the
OL,12,Fwitnesses, and the panel, accept is
OL,13,Fthe case); the adjustment disorder was
OL,14,Fcaused by stress; he has worked to
OL,15,Fmanage stress and no longer presents
OL,16,Fanything more than a low risk of harm
OL,17,Fto the public, if that."
OL,26,@oD@AOUyD@XO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1778602268
OL,3,CBA Pilot who bludgeoned wife to death
OL,4,Cand dumped her body in park, denied
OL,5,Cparole
OL,7,FBefore reaching its decision, the
OL,8,Fpanel carried out a fact-finding
OL,9,Fexercise which concluded that Brown
OL,10,Fhad threatened his wife with a knife
OL,11,Fin July 2007, and that there were
OL,12,F"strong indications of controlling
OL,13,Fbehaviour within the marriage".
OL,15,FAfter the exercise, Brown sacked his
OL,16,Flegal team and refused to attend the
OL,17,Fparole board hearing, instead
OL,18,Fproviding a 37-page written statement.
OL,26,@tD@AOUuD@^O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1778602268
OL,3,CBA Pilot who bludgeoned wife to death
OL,4,Cand dumped her body in park, denied
OL,5,Cparole
OL,7,FBrown was originally due to be
OL,8,Freleased in 2023 after serving half
OL,9,Fhis sentence, but this was blocked by
OL,10,Fthen-justice secretary Alex Chalk, who
OL,11,Fused legal powers to refer the case to
OL,12,Fthe Parole Board.
OL,14,FMs Simpson's mother, Diana Parkes,
OL,15,Fsaid she was "incredibly relieved" by
OL,16,Fthe panel's decision.
OL,18,F"We have all lived with the fear that
OL,19,Fthis might not be the case but thank
OL,20,Fgoodness it was unanimously agreed he
OL,21,Fshould not be released," she said.
OL,26,@wD@NOUwD@bO]zD@AOU}D@XO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1778602268
OL,3,CBA Pilot who bludgeoned wife to death
OL,4,Cand dumped her body in park, denied
OL,5,Cparole
OL,7,F"My daughter would have been 62 last
OL,8,FWednesday 6th May, and, of course, we
OL,9,Fremember her as the beautiful and
OL,10,Fvivacious woman she was at 46. That is
OL,11,Fhow I will always remember her.
OL,13,F"Should Brown have been let out, then
OL,14,FI am glad to have played an
OL,15,Finstrumental part in calling on the
OL,16,FGovernment to introduce robust,
OL,17,Fmandatory restriction zones for
OL,18,Fperpetrators."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1778602268
OL,3,CBA Pilot who bludgeoned wife to death
OL,4,Cand dumped her body in park, denied
OL,5,Cparole
OL,7,FMs Simpson's best friend, Hetti
OL,8,FBarkworth-Nanton, said: "I am
OL,9,Fprofoundly relieved by the Parole
OL,10,FBoard's decision... we have all lived
OL,11,Funder a cloud of fear, a fear that
OL,12,Ftoday, at last, has been lifted.
OL,26,@pD@YOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1778602268
OL,3,CBA Pilot who bludgeoned wife to death
OL,4,Cand dumped her body in park, denied
OL,5,Cparole
OL,7,F"This outcome is not accidental. It is
OL,8,Fthe result of our preparedness to
OL,9,Fcampaign, the extraordinary support of
OL,10,Fthe public and the media, the
OL,11,Fwillingness of politicians to listen,
OL,12,Fthe scrutiny shown by the Ministry of
OL,13,FJustice in their review of this case,
OL,14,Fand the independent rigour of the
OL,15,FParole Board's investigation.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1778602268
OL,3,CBA Pilot who bludgeoned wife to death
OL,4,Cand dumped her body in park, denied
OL,5,Cparole
OL,7,F"We now need to ensure that rigorous,
OL,8,Frisk-based sentencing is applied at
OL,9,Fall times, and that public protection
OL,10,Fis a shared responsibility for
OL,11,Feveryone working with dangerous
OL,12,Foffenders."
OL,14,FFormer justice secretary Sir Robert
OL,15,FBuckland said: "I am pleased and
OL,16,Frelieved that the Parole Board has
OL,17,Frejected this application.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@KO]wD@POU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1778602268
OL,3,CBA Pilot who bludgeoned wife to death
OL,4,Cand dumped her body in park, denied
OL,5,Cparole
OL,7,F"I am glad that the legislation that I
OL,8,Fsponsored as Lord Chancellor to limit
OL,9,Fautomatic release in certain serious
OL,10,Fcases has made a real difference."
OL,12,FCarrie Johnson, who has supported the
OL,13,Ffamily, and is a survivor of serial
OL,14,Frapist John Worboys, said: "Today's
OL,15,Fdecision will be a huge relief to
OL,16,FJoanna's friends and family.
OL,18,F"Joanna's loved ones have spent years
OL,19,Ffighting with extraordinary courage
OL,20,Fand determination to ensure justice is
OL,21,Fdone.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@bO]vD@\OUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G12/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41913
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1778602268
OL,3,CBA Pilot who bludgeoned wife to death
OL,4,Cand dumped her body in park, denied
OL,5,Cparole
OL,7,F"They shouldn't have had to fight as
OL,8,Fhard as they did ` but today's verdict
OL,9,Fshows at least that it has been worth
OL,10,Fit."
OL,12,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,13,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,14,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,15,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,16,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,17,Fbelow...
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@DO]
